<div class="article pbl right-col size3of4 cf">



        <h1 class="header-skin header-structure">Contact the HIC</h1>


    <div class="relative ">


            <div class="content-block">

<p>For more information on the Conservatoire's Historical Instrument Collection please contact the Instrument Custodian Martin Perkins on +44 (0)121 331 7211, or email <a href="mailto:martin.perkins@bcu.ac.uk">martin.perkins@bcu.ac.uk</a>.</p>
<p>For enquiries relating to directly to Birmingham Conservatoire, <a href="/pme/conservatoire/contact-us">please use the Conversatoire's main contact details</a>.<br></p>
            </div>

